===Tamllayt ittawsn===
Tammallayt ittawsn s [[tafransist]] (tourisme solidaire). anawad ntmallayt tra ɣu umallay ay sen is irra timisar n mid ddar baḥra urilliyad, isn iɣ izri tmizarat iqqand a ggis ɣtggmma ni imzdaɣn, icc tiramn sn isɣ tiɣawsiwin li skarn imzdaɣnad, ɣaylli ra yaws, if atig itnunnac ntmizarad du du afganes. Nzdar anna mast taryalin li di ittawi umallyad fulkint bahra idowarn, yli f midn nes as si skern iɣarasn, d ma rayyaws itmazirt ad tal ixfenes.

===Tinunnac n tmallayt===
Tinunnac n tmllayt gant kullu tiwuriwin d tiɣawsiwin li dis zdinin. ilin gisnt tigmma ntusdɣt umallay, d isensa , tuzdaɣ, d iduwarn n tmallayt, ..S [[tafransist]](Métiers de tourisme). 

